description:
Series One includes three optical spinning tops. These tops are 4-1/8 inches wide. Printed on 24 pt. coated cardstock. The spindles are laser cut out of recycled 24 pt. coated, printed stock.

The three tops in this series include:

• A geometric flower design that forms purple and green when spun;

• A design based on a bauhaus top in strong colors that flash as it spins;

• A circling design based on a work by Marcel Duchamp where the red and black rings seem to rise above the card when spun at slow speeds.

The back of the tops have a plain white uncoated surface which you can color to make your own spinners using markers, pens, or stickers. An extra set of spindles is included in case your first set gets tired.

